ot able to conceive a baby then she should fast for 7 days and every day at the time of iftar she should recites YAA MU-SAWWE-RO 21 times with pure heart and blow on water and drink it so then Allah (swt) will give her a righteous child. It will be much better if this ritual is done by both husband and wife.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Jis aurat ko aulaad na hoti ho to usey chahiye keh 7 din roza rakkhe aur roz iftar ke waqt 21 martaba sachche dil se YAA MU-SAWWE-RO padh kar paani par dam (blow) kare aur pee-le to Khuda wande aalam us ko farzand’e saaleh (neyk farzand) ataa farmaayega. Agar is amal ko mard aur aurat (miya-biwi) dono hi anjaam de to aur ziyadah behtar hai.", "UrduDescription": "جس عورت کو اولاد نہ ہوتی ہو تو 7 دن روزہ رکھے اور ہر روز افطار کے وقت 21 مرتبہ صدق دل سے ’’یَا مُصَوِّرُ‘‘  پڑھ کر پانی پر دم کرے اور پی لے تو خداوند عالم اس کو فرزند صالح عطا فرمائے گا۔  اگر اس عمل کو مرد وعورت دونوں ہی انجام دیں تو اور زیادہ بہتر ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "Arab